data.enText: connected with one of the large areas that some countries are divided into, with its own local government

data.chText: 都城以外的；首都以外的
data.enText: connected with the parts of a country that do not include the capital city

data.chText: 心胸狭隘的；守旧的；迂腐的
data.enText: unwilling to consider new or different ideas or things

data.chText: 都城以外的人；乡巴佬；外乡人
data.enText: a person who lives in or comes from a part of the country that is not near the capital city

simple_means.memory_skill: province 省 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 偏狭的；地方性的

tr: (Roman Catholic Church) an official in charge of an ecclesiastical province acting under the superior general of a religious order
example: the general of the Jesuits receives monthly reports from the provincials

tr: characteristic of the provinces or their people
example: in that well-educated company I felt uncomfortably provincial

tr: of or associated with a province

value.def: Provincial means connected with the parts of a country away from the capital city.

example.ex: Jeremy Styles, 34, was the house manager for a provincial theatre for ten years.
example.tran: 杰里米·斯泰尔斯，34岁，在一家地方剧院担任了10年经理。

example.ex: ...in Rasht, the provincial capital of Gilan province.

value.def: If you describe someone or something as provincial, you disapprove of them because you think that they are old-fashioned and boring.

example.ex: He decided to revamp the company's provincial image...
example.tran: 他决心一改公司保守落后的形象。

example.ex: The audience was dull and very provincial.
example.tran: 观众既呆板又非常守旧。

value.def: A provincial is someone who comes from a part of a country away from the capital city.

example.tran: 欧文死的时候是一个不为人知的外乡人。

rootsaffixes.indicate: 表形容词，“具有…的，属于…的”
rootsaffixes.title: -ial

partsOfSpeech.dec: bene 好 + fic 使…的，产生…的，具有某种性质的 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 有益的
commerce 商业 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 商业的
confident 确信的 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 秘密的
con 共同 + gen 产生 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 产生共同点 → 意气相投的
face 面孔 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 面孔的；面部用的
im 不 + part 部分 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 不偏向任何一部分 → 公平的
judic 法律 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 法庭的
president 总统，校长 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 总统（职位）的
province 省 + ial 具有…的，属于…的 → 偏狭的；地方性的
